{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game introduction</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The goal of this game is to build a towering tower of ascension</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Besides aiming for higher scores</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">the main objective of the game is to give the Megami &quot;pleasure&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After experiencing pleasure</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">the Megami will reward players with &quot;Megami Coins&quot; based on their scores</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When choosing skills, during game over, and when reaching high altitude, you can see the different appearances of the Megami </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015270/extras/20240502-1.jpg?t=1737341160\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every 10 layers stacked with &quot;bar&quot; will trigger the skill selection interface</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the selection interface, three out of 6 Megami skills will randomly appear</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players must choose one skill from them</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some skills' effects will last until the next skill selection</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While some skills' effects will last until the game over</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015270/extras/20240406-5.jpg?t=1737341160\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Summon Megami","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3015270/6db6ab7e2ec4ec8340c321d8084133717a074301.jpg"},{"name":"Challenge again","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3015270/526d86eb637bda04be328c8b43ccd6744979bc99.jpg"},{"name":"Funny depth","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steam