 goddess experiences pleasure, she will reward the player with 'Goddess Coins' based on the score. You can see different appearances of the goddess when selecting skills, at the end of the game, and upon reaching great heights."},"detailed_description":"<h1>\ud83d\ude85 ADD IN WISHLIST\ud83d\ude85</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game introduction</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The goal of this game is to build a towering tower of ascension</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Besides aiming for higher scores</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">the main objective of the game is to give the Megami &quot;pleasure&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After experiencing pleasure</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">the Megami will reward players with &quot;Megami Coins&quot; based on their scores</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When choosing skills, during game over, and when reaching high altitude, you can see the different appearances of the Megami </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015270/extras/20240502-1.jpg?t=1737341160\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every 10 layers stacked with &quot;bar&quot; will trigger the skill selection interface</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the selection interface, three out of 6 Megami skills will randomly appear</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players must choose one skill from them</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some skills' effects will last until the next skill selection</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While some skills' effects will last until the game over</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015270/extras/20240406-5.jpg?t=1737341160\" /></p>","developers":["SiGMAGURO"],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"descript